  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Summary】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>What on earth is this school?! </strong></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/e3c7e7affbee9a1bb9523966f90b4832.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weird encounters happened to Natsumi on the first day of her transference</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Counseling Teacher looking for trouble, the Principal with religious fanaticism, and Classmates with absurd common sense ...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meeting classmates and teachers with unique personalities at the start of the semester, can she get used to school life from now on?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Controls】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/bdd67ffb76f3c890754c321ca31f341b.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=439 /></span>▲Game Objective: Players must increase their intelligence and stamina to at least 20 within 20 days!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/12ee925355d8b0aebc24cddece4c0105.poster.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/12ee925355d8b0aebc24cddece4c0105.webm?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/12ee925355d8b0aebc24cddece4c0105.mp4?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲Use arrow keys to control Natsumi and use the Z key to interact with classmates and teachers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b083b97e684d422a0fde841e2f89a0f2.poster.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b083b97e684d422a0fde841e2f89a0f2.webm?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b083b97e684d422a0fde841e2f89a0f2.mp4?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲Attend classes and increase knowledge!<br>Although sometimes it might be a self-study period ...?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b75039e8bbd02e8031c532d0841d677d.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=460 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲Because this is an absurd academy, sparring with classmates is a compulsory subject!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b6ad5f1a445b607cc7b5f1f62ad4c753.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲Utilize each function in the academy to its best to improve your abilities!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Protagonist】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/6d0d79ef46176f25cd6085d2f16c5b90.avif?t=1762827506\" width=254 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲Natsumi</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A normal girl. She is living with her granny because her father is working abroad.She just transferred to a new school and is quite nervous.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Side Characters】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/e710bf3bf944b8f21b5261576c7f392d.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=438 /></span></p>",
